headline.print_headline: Endangered Northern White Rhino Dies in Africa
headline.main: Endangered Northern White Rhino Dies in Africa

lead_paragraph: A Czech zoo says a 34-year-old northern white rhinoceros has died in Kenya, further reducing the world's dwindling population of the critically endangered animal.
